  "description": "<p><strong>Job Scope:</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare test data, basic test scenarios and assist in User Acceptance Testing (UAT) of new module to ensure features are working as per expected after deployment to Production Environment</li><li>Check and verify system generated data for CPI across bases and by incomegroup and other series</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>At least a degree in Mathematics or related </li><li>To be familiar with MS Office (Excel, Word, Edge) </li><li>Prior work experience in UAT </li></ul><p><strong>Working Hours: </strong>Mon,Tues,Thurs,Fri: 8.30am to 6pm (8.5 hrs)/ Wed: 8.30am to 5.30pm (8hrs) </p><p><strong>Contract Period: </strong>11 months </p><p><strong>Location:</strong>  North Bridge Road (City Hall) <br /></p><p><strong>Salary:</strong> $4000-$4500/month </p><p>EA License No.: 96C4864</p><p>Reg No.: R26159658 BRANN LEONG CHUN HOE </p>",
